{
  "stem": "7337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even remember that they ever took our names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I may well be wrong-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because they must have had the names in order to put them in the box.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I know that the teacher of the class tried very hard to help my father to find me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't able to trace me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They just could not find a trace of where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in fact, my father started saying Kaddish for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they rounded us up early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put us into-- they didn't say anything but they put us into a truck, drove us to a railway siding, put us back into cattle trucks, and dropped us outside Berlin in a-- on a siding, a railway siding.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no idea where I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But after about three or four hours, I started seeing landmarks that-- I managed to find my way home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had no money on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I certainly couldn't ask anyone where to go, because as a Jew, I could only expect to be mistreated by whoever I would speak to.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we must have looked very neglected anyway, after all that experience.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] after about four hours, I got home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I found my way home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was the 21st of June, 1933.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother fainted when she saw me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as soon as she came around, she phoned for my dad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came home from the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a very emotional reunion, because as I said, he was a very religious man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, this is a miracle that he hadn't ever dreamt of.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
